PrecisAppointment of THOMAS GERARD RIDEOUT, of the City of St. John's, Newfoundland, as a full-time temporary member of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the IMMIGRATION AND REFUGEE BOARD (Montreal Regional Office) who shall hold office during good behaviour for a term of two years beginning September 11, 1991.
